{"tid":2183620,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"檢測套裝工場髒亂不堪","createTime":"2020-09-01T04:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T05:57:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"663b3cc6b6a372faf8eeae5979dd76d5680a81dc","tid":2183620,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:51:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/C4I6ENAWDFHZXPSQJWQJT7XKRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FC4I6ENAWDFHZXPSQJWQJT7XKRU%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7mqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=e9809d44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FC4I6ENAWDFHZXPSQJWQJT7XKRU%2F&h=6a93696c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/C4I6ENAWDFHZXPSQJWQJT7XKRU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n檢測套裝工場髒亂不堪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】由普及社區檢查到高危群組檢測，政府均未經招標欽點私人化驗所進行，質素無從監察。其中為食肆及街市員工和外傭等高危群組檢測病毒的承辦商Prenetics便爆出衞生隱患。本報發現其旗下Circle DNA 的包裝工場垃圾遍地，工人出入不用探熱亦無消毒。食環署承認包裝工場情況「曾有欠理想」，Prenetics聲稱已着手改善。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tIYG6u66iiVeO--3C7x5GtD2SJg=/1329x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/25SO3AUVWRHT5NDK5NAIN5SVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtIYG6u66iiVeO--3C7x5GtD2SJg%3D%2F1329x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F25SO3AUVWRHT5NDK5NAIN5SVDM.jpg&h=16b83767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■檢測套裝包裝工場內，有工人未戴手套及地上留有垃圾。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n滿地垃圾 徒手包裝<br />\n<br />\n本報早前收到投訴，位於鰂魚涌東祥工廠大廈4樓、Prenetics及其子公司Circle DNA的武肺檢測套裝包裝工場，衞生環境惡劣。從相片可見地上滿佈垃圾、有員工無戴手套工作。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者近日往上述工場了解，場面與投訴相片類同。工場位於貨倉內的房間，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n因貨倉及工場與另一迷你倉公司共用一層，記者採訪當日發現檢測套裝的原料一。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳太指倉庫長期非常大塵，工作期間「成日都聽到有人咳同打乞嚏」，以她所見。。。。。。"},{"pid":"087fffcd85fe68d5e96f5059dfb9606dbee928e8","tid":2183620,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"比支那狗用既，是撚但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edd712dcfef1ba0258ac6ec7f43add381225788","tid":2183620,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9703926c30cf2e9d2949f90175bb7c1582df62b2","tid":2183620,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"估撚到<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe8c6c8ce6f86385411424eebc935b671aacbbf","tid":2183620,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:02:58.000Z","msg":"最好有愛滋添  反正都關我撚事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1563ef0792c7eba194f353658bd0e741f0551d33","tid":2183620,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7262e75f782e3f2b95fb18c9e6dfa3f6bf58dce4","tid":2183620,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"得班傻閪藍絲同支那賤畜先會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f27168a9acde93c6d393789146effd72036a305","tid":2183620,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"是9旦啦！都唔關我事！"},{"pid":"c0e95f7d739123efff4a0874a7249cd2105f45e5","tid":2183